913
00:42:24,958 --> 00:42:28,791
♪ <i>It's the perfect home
For the rest of our lives</i> ♪

914
00:42:28,875 --> 00:42:31,458
♪ <i>Loud Castle, Loud Castle</i> ♪

915
00:42:31,541 --> 00:42:34,166
♪ <i>Yell, stretch, spreading out
